1
00:00:07,924 --> 00:00:09,718
Of all things, why fall on your face?

2
00:00:12,804 --> 00:00:14,180
It's fine

3
00:00:14,472 --> 00:00:15,849
It's nothing. Why put medicine on it?

4
00:00:17,058 --> 00:00:19,060
Hold still. You'll get a scar

5
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:23,815
Ah...

6
00:00:25,525 --> 00:00:26,234
Such a baby

7
00:01:00,977 --> 00:01:02,520
- I dreamt about Lee Jaewon again

8
00:01:03,897 --> 00:01:05,398
- My first love at 18

9
00:01:06,775 --> 00:01:08,276
- still hasn't faded

10
00:01:23,541 --> 00:01:24,501
- Dojin

11
00:01:25,335 --> 00:01:26,336
Hello

12
00:01:27,670 --> 00:01:29,005
Oh... yeah...

13
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:31,508
Hi, Hayeon

14
00:01:33,802 --> 00:01:35,178
It's Kim Hayeong

15
00:01:36,763 --> 00:01:37,889
I know, Hayeong

16
00:01:39,182 --> 00:01:41,309
We even sat next to each other
at the freshman welcome party

17
00:01:41,893 --> 00:01:43,686
Not knowing my name is a bit harsh

18
00:01:45,730 --> 00:01:47,899
Oh... I know

19
00:01:51,986 --> 00:01:54,697
You didn't forget you promised to buy me drinks, right?

20
00:01:57,117 --> 00:01:57,992
Huh?

21
00:01:59,244 --> 00:02:00,161
Did I say that?

22
00:02:01,788 --> 00:02:02,705
Wow

23
00:02:03,414 --> 00:02:04,749
Don't tell me you forgot

24
00:02:06,376 --> 00:02:07,252
Sorry

25
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:08,086
Hey,

26
00:02:08,628 --> 00:02:10,547
you forget that, of all things?

27
00:02:10,797 --> 00:02:12,549
You should buy her a drink today

28
00:02:16,845 --> 00:02:17,554
Well...

29
00:02:21,933 --> 00:02:22,767
Oh...

30
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:27,981
I guess you don't feel comfortable
having drinks alone with me

31
00:02:33,486 --> 00:02:34,487
Then,

32
00:02:34,821 --> 00:02:36,322
the three of us can drink together

33
00:02:37,657 --> 00:02:38,700
I'm fine with that

34
00:02:39,075 --> 00:02:40,118
What about you, Dojin?

35
00:02:45,790 --> 00:02:47,208
Yeah, let's drink today

36
00:02:47,584 --> 00:02:49,377
I'll come after class ends,

37
00:02:49,586 --> 00:02:50,503
so go ahead and wait for me

38
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:51,838
Yay!

39
00:03:04,684 --> 00:03:06,186
Hayeong, where's Minje?

40
00:03:07,228 --> 00:03:08,229
Oh

41
00:03:09,355 --> 00:03:10,064
Well...

42
00:03:10,815 --> 00:03:13,651
He said something urgent came up, so he left first

43
00:03:15,778 --> 00:03:17,488
Seriously, Kim Minje

44
00:03:19,407 --> 00:03:21,159
We can just drink by ourselves

45
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,660
I already ordered some snacks, too

46
00:03:24,537 --> 00:03:25,330
Oh,

47
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:26,414
okay

48
00:03:42,764 --> 00:03:43,932
Take it easy

49
00:03:45,516 --> 00:03:47,101
I can hold my drinks well

50
00:03:48,019 --> 00:03:49,229
How much can you drink?

51
00:03:49,979 --> 00:03:51,981
Um... two bottles?

52
00:03:52,649 --> 00:03:55,109
But if I'm drinking with someone handsome,

53
00:03:55,109 --> 00:03:55,902
maybe three!

54
00:03:57,612 --> 00:03:58,821
I'll make it three for tonight

55
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:25,014
So how's school life?

56
00:04:26,808 --> 00:04:27,809
Hmm

57
00:04:29,435 --> 00:04:31,938
Being a college student is so great

58
00:04:33,022 --> 00:04:34,857
Final year of high school was really tough

59
00:04:35,608 --> 00:04:36,192
Yeah?

60
00:04:36,442 --> 00:04:38,861
As a freshman, just keep having fun

61
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:45,576
I thought once I became a college student,
I'd drink, go clubbing, travel abroad,

62
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:50,999
and finally start dating
Those hopes helped me endure high school

63
00:04:51,499 --> 00:04:52,875
So how many of those have you actually done?

64
00:04:53,584 --> 00:04:54,544
Hmm...

65
00:04:54,544 --> 00:04:56,587
Drinking, clubbing

66
00:04:57,755 --> 00:05:00,216
Oh, I'm planning to travel abroad during break

67
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:04,512
I haven't dated anyone, either

68
00:05:09,767 --> 00:05:10,685
That's surprising

69
00:05:11,102 --> 00:05:12,478
I thought you'd be popular

70
00:05:18,693 --> 00:05:19,944
I didn't say I wasn't

71
00:05:22,071 --> 00:05:23,114
What's your ideal type?

72
00:05:24,866 --> 00:05:26,075
- Hmm...

73
00:05:27,493 --> 00:05:29,329
- Eyes with deep double eyelids

74
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:33,750
- A high nose bridge, and looks pretty

75
00:05:35,126 --> 00:05:37,837
Someone cute, sincere, and is considerate

76
00:05:38,629 --> 00:05:40,757
Someone who hands me tissues right when I need them,

77
00:05:41,174 --> 00:05:43,384
and refills my water glass when it's empty

78
00:05:44,093 --> 00:05:46,512
Someone warm and thoughtful like that

79
00:05:50,641 --> 00:05:52,643
You seem to have a clear preference

80
00:05:56,689 --> 00:05:57,565
What about you?

81
00:05:58,608 --> 00:05:59,525
Me?

82
00:06:01,069 --> 00:06:03,321
I don't really have a type

83
00:06:05,198 --> 00:06:07,992
They say people with no type are the pickiest

84
00:06:09,035 --> 00:06:12,413
Well... I'm not that picky

85
00:06:13,539 --> 00:06:15,041
You know what they say about you?

86
00:06:16,417 --> 00:06:18,878
They said they've never seen you date anyone

87
00:06:23,174 --> 00:06:23,925
True...

88
00:06:25,968 --> 00:06:27,929
Why can't I date, huh?

89
00:06:31,557 --> 00:06:35,728
- I can't because I'm still holding onto my first love

90
00:06:37,355 --> 00:06:38,731
- like an idiot...

91
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,526
I heard people asked you out a few times,

92
00:06:42,568 --> 00:06:43,903
but you turned them all down

93
00:06:46,864 --> 00:06:48,908
Where do you hear all this stuff?

94
00:06:49,492 --> 00:06:50,660
Since you reject them all,

95
00:06:50,910 --> 00:06:53,496
there's even a rumor you like guys

96
00:06:58,042 --> 00:07:00,420
It's not... true, is it?

97
00:07:02,296 --> 00:07:03,965
Hmm

98
00:07:04,924 --> 00:07:06,676
I do like a handsome guy

99
00:07:53,055 --> 00:07:54,515
- What he's up to,

100
00:07:55,766 --> 00:07:56,893
- whether he's even alive,

101
00:07:58,561 --> 00:08:00,104
- I just want to know how he's doing...

102
00:08:14,827 --> 00:08:16,370
- I miss him

103
00:08:50,363 --> 00:08:51,948
What... what time is it?

104
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:56,494
What?

105
00:08:56,911 --> 00:08:59,914
I have a presentation today
I'm in trouble!

106
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:15,555
I'm sorry

107
00:09:16,264 --> 00:09:17,515
- Are you okay?

108
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,601
Lee Jewon?

109
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:35,449
Kim Dojin?

